{"tid":2487980,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湯家驊指朋友之間公開地方談論投票意向應該不受影響","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T03:51:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"915b50275042a1fc76b9af109e390e3e2fd135ee","tid":2487980,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:32:14.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊表示，法例有規定，即使特首選舉只有一名候選人，都要取得過半數票才能當選，如果因有人公開呼籲，令候選人無法取得過半數票，無法選出特首是好大的事，今次將公開活動呼籲他人不投票、投白票或廢票，視作非法行為，既是針對有關情況，亦是回應全國人大常委的相關要求，市民不用大驚小怪。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，個人是有自由選擇投票與否或是否投白票，認為有關法例主要針對有組織、公開呼籲和有廣泛影響的行為，屬於破壞選舉，相信三兩知己在地鐵及巴士站等公開地方談論投票意向的行為，應該不會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n至於在社交媒體講述自己的投票決定，是否有機會違法，湯家驊表示，不應該嘗試鑽空子，避過法律規管，這種態度並不可取，社會亦不應該接受。他表示，法庭會考慮相關人士的意圖和有否合理辯解等因素作平衡，相關的立法在政治上和道德上都是正確，相信不會被濫用。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在新修訂下，選委會的組成和選民基礎亦有好大改動，湯家驊認為，是回應過去兩年香港發生極不愉快事件的結果，認為中央在國家和制度層面以及社會安全等方面，都對泛民失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n本身是資深大律師的湯家驊認為，過往選委會的法律界被民主派壟斷，估計在新修訂下，民主派可取得10至12席，他又認為，改動後令選委會變成更廣泛性及代表性的團體，並非絕不可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585691-20210414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585691-20210414.htm&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11EcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=20270d53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585691-20210414.htm&h=f1b351c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585691-20210414.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b39fb961ecf96210e8272f433dceb16f574029c2","tid":2487980,"uid":18477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNtXqkUK6zQ1x7tJRwD2mH8RWTKNjuD3hLggYaMuxVa3N?filename=CL6Tz93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCL6Tz93.jpg&h=149944a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8abee37bb8cd939db1df203d2311fbd9d9034b6","tid":2487980,"uid":112581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:33:43.000Z","msg":"湯家驊係淋病 律政狗定狗官？"},{"pid":"48e5befbf1a99f4d2420a07a38e81d12e0710363","tid":2487980,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:34:00.000Z","msg":"應該要設批鬥熱線<br />\n互相舉報先岩"},{"pid":"0ff6bb5c1cf6762b1d6403766db55bc37e675a63","tid":2487980,"uid":282930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">應該</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想俾個氹人踩？"},{"pid":"c42b042d5d246cee157da0816a4baf31646538f6","tid":2487980,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"湯渣夠話初選唔會犯法啦"},{"pid":"597d6420d3480259d958aef0a14795a770391a8b","tid":2487980,"uid":260271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"上次9 up完過一晚就縮返去佢老母個閪度ge人<br />\n有咩好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2828a89152953276491b8dcd2e153f80538870e3","tid":2487980,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"我Facebook 講自己投白票都唔得？"},{"pid":"3088084d1645db916eac266ccd1db390bc69a155","tid":2487980,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"「白票」呢個詞語已經變咗同光時一樣"},{"pid":"0937c6f4a0247cc1a29e9e4ef2ca01beefb5ad99","tid":2487980,"uid":126100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 初選問哂D官都冇人 stop , 但半年後先犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eca5e567ff1fcea9cf03712090b98f6b4b874c2","tid":2487980,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"佢 d 風算狗掃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /